project.description: This job does a cleanup of workspace of all jobs

hudson.tasks.BatchFile.command:
REM This deletes the workspace of jobs on 54 machine
xcopy /S /I /E %WIN_GIT_DIR%\harvester\src\scripts\kill_open_handle.py . /Q /Y xcopy /S /I /E %WIN_GIT_DIR%\harvester\src\scripts\handle.exe . /Q /Y cd %workspace%
python kill_open_handle.py v:\slavejenkins\workspace\Windows32_msvc10 python kill_open_handle.py v:\slavejenkins\workspace\Windows32_msvc9 python kill_open_handle.py v:\slavejenkins\workspace\Windows64_msvc9
rmdir /q /s v:\slavejenkins\workspace\Windows32_msvc10 rmdir /q /s v:\slavejenkins\workspace\Windows32_msvc9 rmdir /q /s v:\slavejenkins\workspace\Windows64_msvc9
